name: Selfie girl
description: People have always been interested in watching someone else's life. TV shows, reality shows and social networks are based on this. And a selfie gives a great opportunity to touch the world of a particular person, even if you don't know each other. My picture shows a girl who is ready to openly share a part of her world with those who look at her through the screen. Based on original physicial acrylic on canvas painting.
